videos.description: Matt Mooney comes up with the steal and finds Jarrett Culver on the break for the easy two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Mooney steal turns into Culver fastbreak dunk

videos.description: Brandone Francis gets the steal and takes off to the rack to score using a nice reverse layup to get around the defense.
videos.headline: Francis makes nice reverse layup after steal

videos.description: Jarrett Culver beats the shot clock by using a step-back move to drain a 3-pointer in the face of the defender.
videos.headline: Culver splashes step-back 3-pointer to beat buzzer
